01:53:11.240 --> 01:53:13.790
you now change it.

01:53:13.790 --> 01:53:17.020
That signal processing has to change.

01:53:17.020 --> 01:53:20.400
And as that signal processing changes,

01:53:20.400 --> 01:53:23.350
acutely there's a change.

