It seems to work.

01:53:47.370 --> 01:53:50.270
Now, it doesn't have a permanent change,

01:53:50.270 --> 01:53:51.990
but when I'm getting up to bat

01:53:51.990 --> 01:53:53.570
or getting up to the first tee or getting

01:53:53.570 --> 01:53:56.200
to give a big talk or
