Well, if you take a normal
magnesium supplement

02:12:13.826 --> 02:12:16.640
that you can buy at the pharmacy,

02:12:16.640 --> 02:12:19.400
it doesn't cross the gut very easily.

02:12:19.400 --> 02:12:20.670
